    "content": "<!-- AI-IMAGE: articles-hero-bg | Articles/blog page hero. Clean editorial image suggesting oral health education.\n       SEARCH KEYWORDS: dental articles, oral health education, editorial dental imagery, clinician reading.\n       REQUIREMENTS: Landscape, minimum 1920x800, professional quality.\n       FALLBACK: Any clinical or educational-feeling wide shot.\n       INSTRUCTION: Replace ONLY the url() value inside the section's background-image style; keep the linear-gradient overlay intact. Do not render this as an <img> element. -->\n<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero relative w-full min-h-[560px] md:min-h-[680px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-24 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat text-ivory\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15,23,42,0.75), rgba(15,23,42,0.55), rgba(15,23,42,0.85)), url('https://picsum.photos/1920/1080?random=90');\">\n\n  <div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center flex flex-col items-center\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-eyebrow text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans\">Articles & Resources</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h1 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-heading font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-medium leading-[1.1] mb-6 md:mb-8\">\n      Stay Informed About Your Dental Health\n    </h1>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-subtext text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl font-sans\">\n      Expert insights on dental care, oral health tips, and the latest treatment options from our experienced team. Stay up to date with the information that matters most for your smile.\n    </p>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-body text-base leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl font-sans\">\n      From preventive care basics to understanding complex procedures, our articles are written to help you make informed decisions about your dental health. Browse our latest resources below.\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\">\n\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: cta-label | Choose label by business.category:\n       - Endodontist / Endodontics → \"Book Appointment\"\n       - Orthodontist / Orthodontics → \"Schedule a Consultation\"\n       - Default / other dental → \"Request a Consultation\"\n       Apply the same label consistently across header, body, and footer CTAs for this site. -->\n\n      <a href=\"/consultation\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-hero-component-cta inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-opacity hover:opacity-90 font-sans bg-primary\">\n        <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z\"/></svg>\n        Request a Consultation\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
